Package: ising
Type: Package
Title: Fit MTP2 Ising models
Version: 0.2.3
Author: Kim Daniel Jakobsen
Authors@R: 
    person("Kim Daniel", "Jakobsen", , 
           "kim.jakobsen@jc-aps.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0086-9980"))
Maintainer: Kim Daniel Jakobsen <kimmsn@jc-aps.dk>
Description: Compute the maximum likelihood estimator in Ising models with or 
    without MTP2 restrictions and/or Markov restrictions. Can handle estimates 
    on the boundary of the parameter space. Also has a function to calculate 
    likelihood ratio test statistics using multiple cores.
